All new Rock/Megaman game! - Umex 11:58 am 10-19-00
</table></div>

<div class=itemtext>
There's a new Rock/Megaman game coming to the Gameboy Advance. It's called Megaman EXE, and it's an RPG. The only problem I find with it, is, what kind of Megaman game is a turn based battle system?<br> We'll have to wait to see.<br><br> For the whole shebang of info, go here: <a href="http://pocket.ign.com/previews/15252.html">IGN Pocket</a>
